		<!-- Household Support Fund. -->

		<category>
			<pattern>WHAT IS HOUSEHOLD SUPPORT</pattern>
			<template>
				The Household Support Fund is a measure that provides payments to help households with essential loving expenses like food, clothing and utilities.
This funding is available from 1 April 2022 to 30 September 2022. It is distributed through local councils.
Those who wish to apply must do so through their local council
